v2.0.0

## Changes
- Drop support for Nix
  - Remove `nix-implementation` option
- Rename all options in action to be prefixed with `lix` instead of `nix`, to reflect support
- Remove the flake in the repo; switch to a classic `default.nix`-based project
  - Dependency management now done with [npins](https://github.com/andir/npins)
- Restructure internal release process to be easier to maintain